<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٦٩٤ - حَدِيثٌ <span class="c2">(حم)</span> : <span class="c1">" الْحَجَرُ الأَسْوَدُ مِنَ الْجَنَّةِ "</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">أَحْمَدُ:</span> ثنا يَحْيَى، ثنا شُعْبَةُ، عَنْهُ، بِهَذَا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>